                            <comment id="36025" author="luke" created="Fri, 23 May 2008 09:45:45 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;This looks like a problem with the custom-authentication-provider namespace element. I&apos;ve changed the title accordingly.&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
                            <comment id="36028" author="luke" created="Fri, 23 May 2008 10:38:01 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;I&apos;ve changed the BeanDefinitionDecorator for this element to add a RuntimeBeanReference to the list of registered authentication providers (using the name passed in the BeanDefinitionHolder), rather than the BeanDefinition itself. This should hopefully resolve the issue.&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
